node.text:
Thanks everyone for joining, I had so much fun drawing this and showing you Big Brown! 🐻💕

I get a lot of questions but couldn't answer them all on IG live, I'll try to get them covered in my YouTube videos!

node.text:
✨Art girl makes books✨

When I’m not making comics, I illustrate books! That’s how I make a living. “Everyday, Chemistry” is a cozy book about a mum and daughter finding chemistry reactions in daily activities. Written by @julia_sooy and published by #feiwelandfriends . I had a lot of fun drawing this book.

I also updated my website with book info and purchase links! If you’d like to buy a copy or browse my other books, please head to the link on my profile💕

P.S. Had the idea of having Big Brown introduce the book, a great way to support him otherwise he’d be a pile of bear skin.. 😂

#bonniepangart #childrensbook #childrensbookillustration #everydaychemistry
